# Copy to `.env.local` (or configure in Vercel project settings) to point the
# frontend at a specific backend instance. Leave unset during local dev — the
# Vite proxy in vite.config.ts forwards /api/* to http://localhost:8000.
#
# Production example (Render Free):
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://carbon-pricing-calculator-api.onrender.com/api
